Package: MicroBioMap
Type: Package
Title: Access the microbiome compendium from R
Version: 0.99.13
Description: The MicroBioMap offers access to a dataset including over 
    160,000 samples of publicly available 
    16S rRNA amplicon sequencing data, all processed using the same pipeline 
    and reference database. The main function of the package is to fetch
    the data and parse it into a TreeSummarizedExperiment. Basic documentation
    includes use cases and examples. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    TreeSummarizedExperiment,
    ape
Imports:
    Matrix,
    data.table,
    BiocFileCache,
    R.utils
Encoding: UTF-8
